        "evidence": "<p>Addition of the selected points.</p>",
        "facts": "<p>Increasing BISAP scores also correlate with pancreatitis severity and risk of necrotic pancreatitis. The BISAP performed similarly to more extensive scores, like <calculator id=\"89\">Ranson&rsquo;s Criteria</calculator> and <calculator id=\"1868\">APACHE-II.</calculator></p>",
